==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tychism
<hw>Ty"chism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>ty`chh</grk> fortune, chance + <ets>-ism</ets>.]</ety> <def>Any
theory which conceives chance as an objective reality; esp., a theory of
evolution which considers that variation may be purely
fortuitous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tychonic</ent>⟦br⟧
